cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.CY, cs.IR, cs.CL 

This paper discusses the use of social media and search engine data to assess public health interventions, which falls under the category of social media analysis (cs.SI) and data mining (cs.SD). The methodology used also involves disease modeling (cs.CY) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques. Finally, the paper discusses the qualitative evaluation of the impact estimates, which could fall under the category of natural language processing (cs.CL).
